.description
"Yet Another Kommodity".  Features a sunmouse that only activates when
mouse stops, KeyActivate windows, Click windows to front or back, Cycle
screens with mouse, Mouse and Screen blanking, Close/Zip/Shrink/Enlarge
windows with programmable hotkeys, Activate Workbench by hotkey (to get at
menus when WB obscured), Pop up a palette on front screen, Insert date (in
various formats), KeyClick with adjustable volume, PopCommand key for
starting a command (like PopCLI), Gadtools interface.  All settings
accessible from Workbench tooltypes.  
